  "texts": [
    "The kappa accounts not only for mere agreement but also for agreement by chance.",
    "Of the 475 questions with text choices, the LLM was able to answer 465 (Fig. 2).",
    "Ten questions could not be answered because the LLM was unable to process information from the images.",
    "Of the 342 questions without images administered to examinees and the LLM under the same conditions, 65.9% were answered correctly by the LLM, and a passing score of 62.5% was obtained.",
    "Of the 246 questions with images, 52.0% were answered correctly, even in the absence of any information about the image."
